OL,3,CDriving test cheat attempts soar 47%
OL,4,Cin a year
OL,6,FAttempts to cheat on driving tests in
OL,7,FBritain increased by 47% in a year, an
OL,8,Finvestigation has found, sparking
OL,9,Fconcerns about road safety.
OL,11,FSome 2,844 cases were recorded in the
OL,12,Fyear to the end of September 2025,
OL,13,FDriver and Vehicle Standards Agency
OL,14,F(DVSA) figures obtained by the Press
OL,15,FAssociation news agency show.
OL,17,FThat is up from 1,940 during the
OL,18,Fprevious 12 months, and 1,274 in 2018/
OL,19,F19.
