OL,6,FMotoring research charity the RAC
OL,7,FFoundation said driving test cheats
OL,8,Fare "putting other road users at risk".
OL,10,FThe DVSA attributed the increase in
OL,11,Frecorded cases to a combination of
OL,12,Fmore cheating and better detection.
OL,14,FTechnology-assisted cheating during
OL,15,Ftheory tests, such as using an
OL,16,Fearpiece connected to a concealed
OL,17,Fphone via Bluetooth, made up the
OL,18,Flargest proportion of incidents in
OL,19,F2024/25, with 1,113.
