OL,6,FLearners faced an average waiting time
OL,7,Ffor a test of 22 weeks in September,
OL,8,Fcompared with about five weeks in
OL,9,FFebruary 2020 before the start of the
OL,10,Fcoronavirus pandemic, when testing was
OL,11,Flargely suspended.
OL,13,FThe DVSA said it has no evidence
OL,14,Flinking cheating to waiting times.
OL,16,FLearners arriving at test centres are
OL,17,Frequired to show their face to check
OL,18,Fit matches their photographic ID.
