OL,6,FMeasures to uncover theory test cheats
OL,7,Fcan include asking candidates to roll
OL,8,Fup their sleeves and show their
OL,9,Fpockets are empty, and a staff member
OL,10,Fpatting them down and waving a
OL,11,Fhandheld metal detector around them.
OL,13,FThe DVSA said it also uses
OL,14,Fintelligence to identify vehicles and
OL,15,Findividuals involved in previous
OL,16,Fcheating attempts.
OL,18,FNinety-six people were prosecuted for
OL,19,Fattempting to cheat driving tests or
OL,20,Fimpersonate candidates in 2024/25, the
OL,21,FDVSA said.
